    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car has been my absolute pride and joy\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and always parked in the garage. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a road trip today, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44900.0,
