    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a flawless Porsche 911 Carrera S, a masterpiece of mechanical harmony. The 3.8L naturally aspirated flat-six exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders, paired with a telepathic 7-speed PDK dual-clutch gearbox. This specimen features the Sport Chrono package and PASM active damping, providing exceptional lateral stability and precise damping control. The limited-slip differential and torque vectoring systems remain in peak factory specification, ensuring razor-sharp turn-in. The undercarriage is clinically clean, with no signs of heat cycling on the exhaust headers or oxidation on the suspension components. This is a true turn-key enthusiast machine with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 47500.0,
